I"l<p>SHAPEIT (Segmented HAPlotype Estimation and Imputation Tools) is a commonly used method for haplotype phasing, mainly developed by Olivier Delaneau. The latest version of the tool is SHAPEIT5, which offers the best accuracy for large cohorts at rare variants.</p>

